24-03-07/</link><description>联合国专利机构周四表示，由于经济不确定性，去年专利申请量下降了近 2%，这是 14 年来的首次下降，并称此举“令人担忧”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:29:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/un-data-global-patent-filings-drop-nearly-2-innovation-falters-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>印度政府小组支持对煤炭进口征收更高的碳税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-government-panel-backs-higher-carbon-tax-coal-imports-2024-03-07/</link><description>印度煤炭部周四表示，印度各部委的一个官员小组呼吁对优质进口煤炭征收更高的碳税，同时降低国内煤炭的价格，以减少污染燃料的出货量。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:17:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-government-panel-backs-higher-carbon-tax-coal-imports-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：欧洲央行会议气氛更加明朗，日元打击日经指数</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-07/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:08:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>国会禁止 TikTok 或迫使中国剥离的新举措势头强劲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-push-congress-ban-tiktok-or-force-chinese-divestiture-gains-steam-2024-03-07/</link><description>美国众议院能源和商业委员会预计将于周四就立法进行投票，给予中国字节跳动六个月的时间从短视频应用 TikTok 撤资，否则将面临美国禁令。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/new-push-congress-ban-tiktok-or-force-chinese-divestiture-gains-steam-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>印度总理五年来首次访问克什米尔表示，克什米尔已经发生了变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/kashmir-has-been-transformed-indian-pm-says-first-visit-five-years-2024-03-07/</link><description>总理纳伦德拉·莫迪周四表示，喜马拉雅山地区的查谟和克什米尔地区已经发生转变，并与印度其他地区融为一体，并将这一变化归因于印度政府撤销其特殊地位的有争议的决定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 10:22:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/kashmir-has-been-transformed-indian-pm-says-first-visit-five-years-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国新疆高级官员称伊斯兰教“中国化”“不可避免”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-official-chinas-xinjiang-says-sinicisation-islam-inevitable-2024-03-07/</link><description>新疆共产党高级官员周四表示，北京被指控侵犯人权的中国西北部穆斯林占多数的地区的伊斯兰教“中国化”是“不可避免的”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 10:16:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-official-chinas-xinjiang-says-sinicisation-islam-inevitable-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>香港以“迫在眉睫”的风险为由，全速推动新的安全法案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-submit-new-national-security-bill-legislature-this-week-2024-03-07/</link><description>香港政府将于周五向立法机关提交“23条”国家安全法案，可能会进一步镇压这个前英国殖民地的异见人士，香港领导人李家超呼吁“全速”通过该法案。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 09:30:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-submit-new-national-security-bill-legislature-this-week-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>受到制裁打击的油轮Liteyny Prospect停靠在中国以卸载俄罗斯石油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/sanctioned-tanker-liteyny-prospect-docks-china-offload-russian-oil-2024-03-07/</link><description>两名知情人士称，受到制裁打击的俄罗斯油轮“Liteyny Prospect”号已停靠在中国黄骅港，卸货70万桶俄罗斯索科尔原油货物，清理了因莫斯科石油制裁而中断的部分积压货物。贸易。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 08:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/sanctioned-tanker-liteyny-prospect-docks-china-offload-russian-oil-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>印度卢比看涨头寸达到两年多高位；路透调查：亚洲外汇空头坚守阵地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/bullish-positions-indian-rupee-over-two-year-high-asian-fx-bears-hold-ground-2024-03-07/</link><description>路透周四的一项调查显示，由于中国经济复苏的不确定性和全球货币宽松时间表拖延，印度卢比的看涨押注达到两年半以来的最高水平，而投资者对大多数亚洲货币维持看跌头寸。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:47:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/bullish-positions-indian-rupee-over-two-year-high-asian-fx-bears-hold-ground-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚总理表示，试图遏制中国只会加剧其不满</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/trying-contain-china-will-only-fuel-its-grievances-says-malaysian-pm-2024-03-07/</link><description>马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣周四在澳大利亚发表讲话时表示，遏制中国崛起的企图只会加剧该国的局势，并在该地区制造不和。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/trying-contain-china-will-only-fuel-its-grievances-says-malaysian-pm-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>日本表示对中俄更密切的军事关系感到严重关切</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan-says-it-is-gravely-concerned-about-closer-military-ties-between-china-2024-03-07/</link><description>日本政府最高发言人周四表示，考虑到日本和该地区的安全，东京对中俄之间更密切的军事合作表示严重关切。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan-says-it-is-gravely-concerned-about-closer-military-ties-between-china-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>随着大型科技公司争先恐后地遵守欧盟规则，调查可能会发生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/big-tech-scrambles-meet-eu-rules-investigations-seen-likely-2024-03-07/</link><description>全球最大的科技公司已经彻底改革了其核心平台服务，以遵守欧盟规则，迫使它们与竞争对手更加公平地竞争，但由于批评它们的努力可能不够充分，未来可能会面临调查。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 06:03:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/big-tech-scrambles-meet-eu-rules-investigations-seen-likely-2024-03-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>